subject: ECE
title: Nanoelectronic Circuits and Systems Project
description: This is a project course, designed exclusively for MEng students completing the Nanoelectronic Circuits and Systems specialization. Students will carry out a research project over one academic term, under the direct supervision of an ECE faculty member from the associated research area. At the end of the term, a written Project Report has to be submitted, which will be evaluated and marked by the Supervisor.
